{"title":"走进童心","authors":["杨德祥"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":6,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进童心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨德祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，“童心未泯”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一座快乐的天桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有童心站岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愁云就不敢笼罩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热爱生活的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是朝气蓬勃的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无瑕的心灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给辉煌与创造。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，“童颜鹤发”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一座幸福的航标，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有童心巡逻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皱纹就不敢抛锚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥抱生活的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是永葆青春的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“童心万岁”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝不是梦中的祈祷！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}